{"tid":244191,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【國泰炒基層】傳國泰後勤基層都炒人！最快周五通知","createTime":"2017-05-15T08:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T10:36:22.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"771d6bcd090c3da410f5b577c045ddb61c4b6da4","tid":244191,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"【新增影片、工會回應】市傳國泰航空（293）後勤將進行大規模裁員！除經理級或以上員工外，有機會涉及基層，消息指受影響員工最快將於5月19日（周五）收到正式通知。<br />\n<br />\n《香港經濟日報》引述消息指出，國泰航空裁員主要針對約1萬名後勤人員，後勤人員中分A、B、C、D、E五級，A為最低級，E級是最高級，之前消息傳出裁員只涉及經理級或以上的C級員工，但報道引述最新消息指，裁員將波及A、B級的基層員工，於第一輪中、高層裁員完成後，下月5至9日會以面試形式，決定A、B級人手的去留。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，最高層、即總監級別（Level E）最快會於5月19日收到正式裁員通知，而經理級或以上員工則於5月22日收到正式通知。據悉國泰會向被裁員工提供「肥雞餐」、最高補償12個月薪金，員工醫療福利在離職後3個月仍可使用，離職1年可繼續購買優惠機票。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空發言人表示，國泰最近公佈將建立更精簡、能迅速應變及更完善的新管理架構。該公司將在適當時候公佈有關變動。另外，國泰空中服務員工會表示，目前裁員未涉及空中服務員，但作為工會，希望公司採其他措施節流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/164507_3dac0547143e9a50fa2604eb07a1e9c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F164507_3dac0547143e9a50fa2604eb07a1e9c9.jpg&h=d3498b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56694995&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56694995%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=50ee0756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56694995%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&h=0fdbfef6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56694995&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515</a>"},{"pid":"61e7ac3164098c4f8c3494af4fbeee9a0ad48ee6","tid":244191,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"國泰越做越衰，都唔知幾耐無坐過佢了，執柒咗佢算數喇"},{"pid":"dba49ff9d647eab8724da671d685ced0db50e383","tid":244191,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"IT狗？"},{"pid":"b2494e8ab1f66af3fe51c874b82332db322175c5","tid":244191,"uid":6227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"坐ECON真係唔洗再揀國泰<br />\n乜柒都CUT"},{"pid":"058b975ecaeda438d25201b75cf80b89554ac0c0","tid":244191,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐ECON真係唔洗再揀國泰<br />\n乜柒都CUT</blockquote><br />\nX2<br />\n上次飛sydney坐完條腰痛到<br />\n以後永不坐cathy or dragon"},{"pid":"6e63cfe94882f3f67b8993d629c32cb929b28140","tid":244191,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:53:53.000Z","msg":"E class =\tit dog"},{"pid":"75522189605bf165b158217d31e73869c2c45595","tid":244191,"uid":64582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"補1年水咁so<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694bf3fa997a95d1c6afd3404167ba91e9ea70e5","tid":244191,"uid":35266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐ECON真係唔洗再揀國泰<br />\n乜柒都CUT</blockquote><br />\n成個航空市場兩極化緊<br />\nService夠好既，好似JAL ANA咁賣到貴一貴都大把人坐<br />\nCX偏偏要走去同廉航開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b12192fc8cd821127bd2bd6835f964b77cb741b","tid":244191,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"玩油輸咗，炒細嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e93fbbf51f59deb7109bbec9f7c5b8015211ed","tid":244191,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>E class =\tit dog</blockquote><br />\n最高級it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder